desc: Old Dog Lures, designed and handcrafted in Townsville Australia from sustainable timber and quality components for Barramundi, Mangrove Jack, Fingermark, Bass, Cod, Queen fish, Giant Trevally, Tuna, Flathead, Jungle Perch and Bream. Every lure is tank tested to ensure quality before leaving the Dog House.

layout.text: Born and bred in Australia to catch fish.
